>*Our goal is for staff to have access to the tools they need to maximise the potential of data and help the department deliver on its data strategy.*

## Who we are

The Analytical Platform team is a joint venture between the Platforms & Architecture team (Justice Digital) the Data Engineering & Data Science team (Data & Analysis division).

Together, we combine our product, technical, and data expertise to deliver a secure platform that enables staff to interrogate their data.

To find someone on the team use People Finder [here](https://peoplefinder.service.gov.uk/teams/analytical-platform)

## Our Service

Users of the Analytical Platform can

- Upload and store data in a secure environment for analytical or reporting purposes
- Transform and model raw data to enable more efficient data processing/analysis
- Automate and schedule data pipelines or transformations
- Access cloud-based analytical & development tools/IDEs with GitHub version control
- Create bespoke dashboards & apps to visualise data that can be shared/published
